<s> As Chetz has pointed out, the linear version is alreday difficult to read, and people would like it to be simplified.  </s>
<s> My personal feeling is that having a single complete document makes referencing more intuitive and makes it clear that all the guidelines apply at the same time, and there are many implicit cross-references, which seems to be a point easily missed.  </s>
